perience.\n\n\n**Refining Mobile Card Updates**\n\nI'm now integrating the mobile fallback cards and incorporating dropdowns within the card, focusing on efficient data display and inline edits on smaller screens. I'm focusing on user experience, and have made mobile interactions streamlined to reflect updates on both small and large screens.\n\n\n**Refining Delivery Owner Display**\n\nI'm now integrating delivery owner details, including the initials badge, within each table row. The code to display initials, using a small rounded badge within the project details, has been implemented. I'm focusing on ensuring it's clearly displayed and consistent across all rows.\n\n\n**Integrating Delivery Owner**\n\nI've just added the display of the delivery owner's initial badge to each table row, using a small, rounded badge within each project's data. I've focused on consistency, so the owner's details are clear across the interface. I've also incorporated those badge changes in the dropdowns.\n\n\n**Refining Desktop Table**\n\nI'm now implementing styling for the desktop table, focusing on hover states and refined borders for improved readability. I am working towards a consistent and premium look, including visual indicators. I've been integrating the visual feedback and icons.\n\n\n**Refining UI Enhancements**\n\nI'm now integrating the desktop styling, focusing on hover effects and borders for a polished look. I've added node counts, 'Quick Edit', and 'Telemetry' actions. I'm also preparing the styling for `handleDeprovision` with confirmation dialogs. Finally, I've incorporated those styling details in `getPhaseColor` and `getStatusStyle`.\n\n\n**Refining Desktop Table**\n\nI'm now implementing styling for the desktop table, focusing on hover states and refined borders for improved readability. I am working towards a consistent and premium look, including visual indicators. I've been integrating the visual feedback and icons.\n\n\n**Refining Component Interactions**\n\n