{"ts":"2026-06-27T05:54:43.471Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"tool","toolName":"submit_and_exit","toolCallId":"0aunb1wy","input":{"summary":"Successfully built the complete GFF AI Internal Project Delivery Management dashboard at `/admin/projects` matching the premium, enterprise-grade UI Quality Constitution.\n\n### Design Details:\n1. **Strategic Narrative**: Engineered a high-fidelity 'command telemetry deck' that maps out active sovereign multi-agent client enclaves, operational phases, active cluster nodes, and SLA ownership.\n2. **Dynamic UI & Metrics Ribbon**: Features 4 custom metric blocks (Active Enclaves, Live Deployments, Active Delivery Risks, SLA Owners) that recalculate dynamically whenever a project is created, modified, or deprovisioned.\n3. **Advanced Multi-Filtering & Fuzzy Search**: Implemented select filters by Client Account, Operational Phase, SLA Status, and Delivery Owner, together with a fuzzy search query bar and an active filters pill indicator with reset actions.\n4. **Desktop Telemetry Grid & Mobile Cards Fallback**:\n   - **Desktop**: A custom, dense, readable table with interactive, clickable status and phase badges that open inline quick-change option dropdowns, a 'Quick Edit' configuration modal, and external logs linkage to `/admin/projects/[id]`.\n   - **Mobile**: Stacks into beautiful bento-styled cards that retain full inline phase/status changers and CRUD actions.\n5. **Interactive Preview Actions (Frontend-Only CRUD)**:\n   - **Provision Enclave Form**: A center-focused dark modal with full validation, descriptions, and warnings to append newly deployed sandbox previews.\n   - **Quick Edit Modal**: Enables modifying active project configurations on the fly.\n   - **Local Status/Phase Updater**: Changes telemetry levels in-place.\n   - **Deprovision Action**: A soft confirmation flow that isolates and removes an enclave loop locally.\n   - **Success Toast Alert**: Animated premium bottom-r